<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,320]" pageId="5" pageNumber="336">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,260,285]" pageId="5" pageNumber="336">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Both sexes: Idiosoma elongated-oval (dorsal shield L/W ratio 1.3–1.4); gnathosomal rostrum long; P-4 stout, L/H 2.4–3.0; female: genital field roundish, L/W 0.95–1.05.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
